      <title>EUSOME</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/evlachos_website/project/eusome/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/evlachos_website/project/eusome/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Role:&lt;/strong&gt; Principal Investigator (PI) for ISI/Athena RC.
&lt;strong&gt;Funding:&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;gt;800k€ (Horizon Europe).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;EUSOME&lt;/strong&gt; project establishes a &amp;ldquo;Living Lab&amp;rdquo; for Advanced Aerial Mobility (AAM). We focus on:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cooperative Sensing:&lt;/strong&gt; Algorithms for UAV swarms to sense the environment collectively.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Digital Twins:&lt;/strong&gt; Real-time synchronization between physical drones and their digital counterparts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experimental Validation:&lt;/strong&gt; Using the Aerial Networks Testbed at ISI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This project bridges the gap between theoretical 6G control algorithms and real-world deployment.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
